# Hoist packages needed by jiti-loaded plugins (openclaw-weixin).
# pnpm strict mode only hoists direct deps by default; OC loads plugins
# via jiti which resolves imports from the project root node_modules.
# Without hoisting, imports like `zod` and `qrcode-terminal` fail with
# "Cannot find module" even though they're in the pnpm store.
public-hoist-pattern[]=qrcode-terminal
public-hoist-pattern[]=zod
